<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink385">
<l>kaṭuṅkaṭ kāḷaiyoṭu neṭuntē rēṟik</l>
<l>kōḷval vēṅkai malaipiṟak koḻiya</l>
<l>vēṟupal laruñcura miṟantaṉa ḷavaḷeṉak</l>
<l>kūṟumiṉ vāḻiyō vāṟuceṉ mākkaḷ</l>
<l>naṟṟō ṇayantupā rāṭṭi</l>
<l>yeṟkeṭut tirunta vaṟaṉil yāykkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O people going [your] way!  May you live long! </l>
<l>Tell my mother devoid of virtue,  </l>
<l>who loved and praised [my] good shoulders, [and then] ruined me: </l>
<l>"She has traversed many different difficult deserts, </l>
<l>leaving behind mountains with strong killer tigers, </l>
<l>having mounted a tall chariot with [her] brutal young man". </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
